import React from 'react'
import {Card, Container, Row, Button} from 'react-bootstrap'

export default function ProductItem() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col>
                    <Card>
                        <Card.Img></Card.Img>
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Card.Title>Test</Card.Title>
                            <Card.Text>Test</Card.Text>
                            <Button variant="primary">Buy Now</Button>
                        </Card.Body>
                    </Card>
                </Col>
            </Row>

        </Container>
    )
}
